folder: Van Duzer Street & Prospect Street, Staten Island, NY
original_title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - Prospect Street
text:
346 Van Duser Street, west side, at the head of Prospect Street, showing the Steuben Club. On Bromley's 1917
aap it is shown as the Elks Club No. 841.
February 9, 1999
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, at a later date.
May 25, 1935
P. L. Sperr
